+
+## Subagent Type Selection
+
+Choose the appropriate `subagent_type` for implementer agents based on the task's primary language or domain:
+
+| Domain / Language      | subagent_type                        |
+|------------------------|--------------------------------------|
+| Rust                   | systems-programming:rust-pro         |
+| Go                     | systems-programming:golang-pro       |
+| Solidity / Web3 / DeFi | blockchain-web3:blockchain-developer |
+| General / other        | general-purpose (default)            |
+
+For code quality reviews of Web3/Solidity code, use `git-pr-workflows:code-reviewer` and additionally dispatch `security-scanning:security-auditor` for a parallel security review.
+
 ## Handling Implementer Status
 
 Implementer subagents report one of four statuses. Handle each appropriately:
